# Version Selector UI Refinement Plan

Optimize the version selection dialog to improve usability and visual appeal, specifically focusing on button visibility, rounded aesthetics, and smooth transitions.

## Proposed Changes

### [Component] Version Selector Dialog

#### [MODIFY] [VersionSelectorDialog.xaml](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/VersionSelectorDialog.xaml)
- **Structure Optimization**: 
  - Ensure the "Confirm" and "Cancel" buttons at the bottom are always visible by properly constraining the central content area's height.
  - Wrap the bottom buttons in a distinct footer border for better visual separation.
- **Header Aesthetics**: Update dynamic header styles to use softer rounded corners (15px) instead of the current sharp corners.
- **Button Fix**: 
  - Increase the `MinWidth` for the "Hide/Folder" button in the top right to prevent text truncation where only "隐" is visible.
  - Adjust margins to ensure it doesn't collide with the close button.
- **Animations**: 
  - Define `Storyboard` resources for the [FolderPanel](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/VersionSelectorPage.xaml.cs#225-238) to animate [Opacity](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/SettingsPage.xaml.cs#303-313) and `Width` during expand/collapse.
  - Implement smooth sliding effects for a premium feel.

#### [MODIFY] [VersionSelectorDialog.xaml.cs](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/VersionSelectorDialog.xaml.cs)
- **Header Logic**: Update [AddVersionCategory](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/VersionSelectorDialog.xaml.cs#107-137) to apply a higher `CornerRadius` to the category headers.
- **Animation Logic**: Replace hard [Visibility](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/SettingsPage.xaml.cs#324-332) toggles with `BeginStoryboard` calls in [ToggleFolderPanel_Click](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/VersionSelectorPage.xaml.cs#225-238).
- **Button Logic**: Ensure button content updates ("隐藏" / "文件夹") are accompanied by smooth transitions.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
- Open the version selector dialog.
- Verify that "确定" (Confirm) and "取消" (Cancel) buttons are visible at the bottom.
- Toggle the "文件夹" (Folder) panel and observe the smooth opening/closing animation.
- Check that the "隐藏" text is fully visible in the top-right button when the panel is open.
- Confirm that version category headers have noticeably rounded corners.
- Confirm that selecting a version correctly enables the "Confirm" button if it was disabled or just that it works.
